{
  "chapter": 90,
  "chapter_summary": "寇仲与徐子陵制定妙计，利用装有尖铁的战船拦腰撞向敌方巨舶。巨鲲帮副帮主卜天志率众执行撞船任务，寇仲与徐子陵则趁乱跃上敌舰展开近身搏斗。徐子陵击退大江会二当家\"虎君\"裴炎，又遭黑衣高手白文原偷袭。寇仲在水底追击并生擒游秋凤，却再次将其释放，二人之间暗生情愫。战后众人发现将军府内藏有内奸，寇仲通过审讯被俘女婢小秋，以巧妙的心理战术逐步套出内奸线索，最终确认了传递情报之人。本章展现了寇仲的智谋与徐子陵的武功，兄弟二人在争霸天下的道路上渐行渐远。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "仲少你别忘了现在是争霸天下，不是去逞强斗狠，要讲点策略才成。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你有甚么妙计呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "记得我们由九江来巴陵那艘战船吗？船头还装了尖铁，若速度够快，保证可把这艘巨无霸硬生生拦腰撞断。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你这小子其实比我还狠，平时却要装成淡泊名利的道学先生。嘻！你不觉得自己今晚很不正常吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "快来吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "卜天志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让我遣人立即通知香将军，若能擒得朱媚，等若废去朱粲一条手臂。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bu_tian_zhi",
      "text": "敌人非是省油灯，必在岸上布有暗哨，你们这么千军万马的掩去，敌人不走就是呆头鸟，副帮主只可依我们的计划行事。你负责撞船，我们负责下水拿人，这叫分工合作，明白吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_bu_tian_zhi",
      "text": "朱媚很厉害吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "卜天志",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "朱媚等若朱粲的脑袋，却貌美如花，毒似蛇蝎，在她的流云袖下，已不知多少英雄好汉饮恨收场。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在水底还有甚么流云袖可施展出来，今趟看她如何美如何狠好了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "卜天志",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "两位公子不但行事出人意表，想出来的方法更是妙想天开，天志受教了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "卜天志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "动手！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "要争霸天下，必须广揽人材，否则纵使有此妙计，我们亦没有能力施行。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你是我在这世上最好的兄弟，既然答应了你要助你取得'杨公宝库'，不积极点怎行？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "同时也是为了素姐，这些人既在香小子府内布有内奸，当然清楚素姐和我们的关系，假若奈何不了我们，说不定会向素姐入手，所以我们必须生擒对方一两个带头的人，交由香小子用刑迫供，务要把内奸寻出，素姐的安全才有保障。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_pei_yan",
      "text": "二当家也要逃命吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_yan",
      "speaker_name": "裴炎",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "杀了你这小子才走也不迟。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wen_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "白文原",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "今趟算你们狠，但终有一天我白文原会好好报答你们。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_you_qiu_feng",
      "text": "凤姐想在江中亲热，还是待上岸再温存呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_qiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "游秋凤",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "杀了我吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_you_qiu_feng",
      "text": "不！我仍要放你！因为我喜欢你的俏样儿，当日贵帮主搂着你的小蛮腰时，累得我都不知多么想当帮主。哈！不过我终不是也抱了你亲了你又摸了你吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_qiu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "游秋凤",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇仲你莫要后悔，有机会我绝不肯放过你的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_you_qiu_feng",
      "text": "其实你是爱上了我，所以才特别恨我，只是你自己不知道吧！我们走着瞧好了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "早已知机逃了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她是我的一个贴身小婢，自今早出门便失去影综。唉！想不到我待她亲如姊妹，她竟会做这种事。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她自幼便侍候我，想不到竟会给人收买了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "text": "她懂武功吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你给人骗了，若我猜得不错，这小婢必是遭了毒手，好使你以为已没有了内奸的问题。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小梅！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是我不好！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你们对素姐确是好得令人没话说。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎样才能把这内奸挖出来碎尸万段呢？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只是他令素姐伤心落泪，我便不肯放过他。给我把那被活擒女婢提来，我保证可从身上得悉内奸的身分。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "text": "姑娘请坐！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "text": "只要你肯答我几个问题，我可以立即放了你，让你好好享受你的大好青春。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "text": "谁不知我寇仲是个好人，你的主子要杀我，并非因为我做过甚么坏事，只为对'杨公宝库'起了贪念，所以你的主子才是坏人。哈！这道理多么简单，不明白的就是笨蛋。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "text": "就让我这好人作出保证，只要你肯答三条问题，我就放了你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "小秋",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若我答了你，但你又硬指我说谎，那……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "text": "是否说谎，大家都心知肚明，例如假若你稍有犹豫的情况，又或说得断断续续，便分明在编故事，那就不用继续下去了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "小秋",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "真的只问三个问题？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "text": "当然！我岂是言而无信的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "小秋",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "只要我没有犹豫，说话更没有断断续续，就可以走了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "text": "就是这样。不过假若你犯上这些错误，我立即废了你武功，并把你卖落最低级的窑子，让你每天至少接十个客，明白吗？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "text": "你叫甚么名字？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "小秋",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我叫小秋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "text": "第一个问题过关了！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "小秋",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇公子请说第二个问题吧！",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "text": "第二个问题是，嘿！你的主子是谁？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "小秋",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "媚公主！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "text": "恭喜姑娘连过两关，答完下个问题后，我会亲自送姑娘出城与家人团聚，最好不要回媚公主那去了。如此声名狼藉的主人，黏上了随时有祸，今趟当作是个教训好哩。",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "小秋",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "公子问吧！",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "text": "昨晚谁把信交给你？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "小秋",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我不知他的名字啊！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "text": "他有多高！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "小秋",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "比我高半个头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu",
      "text": "我知道他是谁了，这便送姑娘离开，不要哭了！",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 369
    }
  ],
